OL,4,G1700FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe new run continues. The week's
OL,6,     Gfinal visit is to Jordan and
OL,7,     GRobin's pub in Somerset. But with
OL,8,     Gone B&Ber dreading the potential
OL,9,     Gof stale ale smell, the hosts
OL,10,     Ghave their work cut out.
OL,11,G1730FCome Dine with Me
OL,12,     GThe new run continues. On the
OL,13,     Gfourth night in Bedfordshire and
OL,14,     GCambridgeshire Shane creates a
OL,15,     Gtriumphant Jamaican menu. And his
OL,16,     Gstrong gin martinis also raise
OL,17,     Gthe bar.
