OL,5,G1800FLove Nature
OL,6,     GThe greater horseshoe bat was
OL,7,     Gonce widespread in the UK but due
OL,8,     Gto habitat loss their numbers
OL,9,     Gplummeted. The Vincent Wildlife
OL,10,     GTrust look after around 50% of
OL,11,     Gthe UK's population.
OL,12,G1805FSusan Calman's Grand Day Out
OL,13,     GSusan visits the South Downs and
OL,14,     GHundred Acre Wood, enjoying
OL,15,     Gscenic views and nostalgia.
